    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      Our tools are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either
      express or implied. We do not guarantee the accuracy, reliability, or
      availability of our services and disclaim any liability for damages
      resulting from their use.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      We reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time.
      Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use
      of our website constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      If you have any questions about these terms, please reach out to us at
      <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline"
